data.description: Motivated Seller! Rare Find on Corner Lot with Fully Fenced Backyard in Gated Solera Chandler Community! Spacious living areas with vaulted ceilings open to great room floor plan. Two generously sized bedrooms on opposite sides of home offer ultimate privacy and convenience. Primary bedroom overlooks backyard with ensuite bath that boasts double sinks, large shower and walk-in closet. Guest bath has walk in Jacuzzi tub. The open kitchen features center island, cozy breakfast nook with bay windows overlooking backyard and includes all appliances. The fully fenced, private backyard features covered patio, lush landscaping and mature trees, 2-citrus! Home is located on North/South facing oversized, corner lot on quiet cul-de-sac street with beautiful grassy park. Enjoy an active adult lifestyle in the amenity-rich Solera Chandler community with biking/walking paths, pickleball and tennis courts, heated pools, fitness, community center with planned daily activities and is adjacent Lone Tree Golf Course. Come visit today!
